00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:07,840
 vjerojatno,

451
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:09,080
 kak se ja ovešćam u tom,

452
00:24:09,080 --> 00:24:10,740
 u tom trenutku.

453
00:24:10,740 --> 00:24:12,200
 I ne mogu reći,

454
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:12,600
 iako,

455
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:14,280
 kako bih rekao,

456
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:17,260
 čitam i učim se o tome stalno i cijeli život,

