00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:51,760
 pa će se truditi, ne pretjerivati,

577
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:54,440
 ali tako inače napravim po antu.

578
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:56,160
 Ali ne znam,

579
00:29:56,160 --> 00:30:00,060
