580
00:30:00,060 --> 00:30:02,500
 i sad prolazi nešto,

581
00:30:02,500 --> 00:30:05,300
 sad malo se bezobrazno prema tebi odnosio.

582
00:30:05,300 --> 00:30:06,960
 Počnu ti reći, na šta je,

