607
00:30:57,280 --> 00:30:57,460
 ono,

608
00:30:57,460 --> 00:30:58,360
 kako balansiram.

609
00:30:58,360 --> 00:31:01,420
 Bitno je čut,

610
00:31:01,420 --> 00:31:02,540
 ono,

611
00:31:02,540 --> 00:31:02,900
 šta,

612
00:31:02,900 --> 00:31:06,080
 šta tebi taj to unutani glas govori o tebi,

613
00:31:06,080 --> 00:31:07,080
 ali s druge strane,

614
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:08,040
 i bit svjestan

615
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:09,560
 te druge osobe.

616
00:31:09,820 --> 00:31:10,600
 Jer ako nisi,

617
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:12,640
 to prelazi u stvarno bez obrazluku

618
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:13,360
 i egoizam.

619
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:13,780
 Znači,

620
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:14,680
 briga me ko si ti,

621
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,320
 šta si ti,

622
00:31:15,320 --> 00:31:15,600
 naš,

623
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:15,820
 ono,

624
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:16,400
 Vinko,

625
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:16,960
 meni je to,

626
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:17,620
 Vinko,

627
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:18,040
 ne znam,

628
00:31:18,040 --> 00:31:20,020
 ja se osjećam da me ne vidiš,

629
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:20,620
 Vinko,

630
00:31:20,620 --> 00:31:20,960
 ono,

631
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:23,840
 ja mislim da mi ne daš dovoljno pozornosti,

632
00:31:23,840 --> 00:31:25,240
 ono će samo bit Vinko,

633
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:25,560
 Vinko,

634
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:25,920
 Vinko,

635
00:31:25,920 --> 00:31:26,160
 naš,

636
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:26,300
 ono,

637
00:31:26,300 --> 00:31:28,400
