909
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:34,660
 iću za time što me vuče,

910
00:38:34,660 --> 00:38:35,780
 ako ću biti nježan,

911
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:36,780
 ću biti nježan,

912
00:38:36,780 --> 00:38:40,520
 iskreno budu situacija i kad sam grub.

913
00:38:40,520 --> 00:38:43,640
 I to mi bude normalno,

914
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:44,460
 i onda kad to prođe,

915
00:38:44,460 --> 00:38:44,920
 skužim,

916
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,840
 pa naš,

917
00:38:46,840 --> 00:38:48,760
 možda nisam morao vikat na malu,

918
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:52,220
 ali me izgurala me do krajnjih granica,

919
00:38:52,220 --> 00:38:59,760
 i onda bacite u tu neku primitivan mozak

920
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:01,380
 gdje ne znaš drugačije.

921
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:03,500
 i onda se vratiš nazad,

922
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:04,020
 pa kao,

923
00:39:04,020 --> 00:39:06,200
 kao je li to način,

924
00:39:06,200 --> 00:39:07,600
 možda obiti isto s time,

925
00:39:07,600 --> 00:39:08,600
 on skuži da ne možeš,

926
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:09,820
 znači da je to čisto neki,

927
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:12,840
 tvoja borba protiv ono nemogućnosti,

928
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:13,900
 i onda je možda muška,

929
00:39:13,900 --> 00:39:14,300
 ne znam,

930
00:39:14,300 --> 00:39:14,960
 okrenca,

931
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:15,500
 nagresija,

932
00:39:15,500 --> 00:39:16,160
 šta god to bila,

933
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:16,600
 ne mislim,

934
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:17,980
 daš nekog lupit,

935
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:18,420
 nego ono,

936
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:19,860
 bit ćeš bezobrazan,

937
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:21,060
 bit ćeš sarkastičan,

938
00:39:21,060 --> 00:39:21,600
 bit ćeš,

939
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,440
 ne znam,

940
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:25,060
 bit ćeš glasni i zavikat ćeš.

941
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:26,700
 tako da,

942
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:27,180
 ne znam,

943
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:28,880
 teška mi je baš ta tema,

944
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:29,600
 iskreno,

945
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:31,820
 o muškarcima.

946
00:39:32,180 --> 00:39:33,800
 kako bi na hrvatski projeli riječ

947
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:35,180
 agreeable,

948
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:39,140
 netko ko previše popušta,

949
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:42,100
 ne zna se zauze za sebe,

950
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:43,600
 ne zna postavi granicu,

951
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:44,460
 kako treba.

952
00:39:44,460 --> 00:39:45,880
 A možda da,

953
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:48,060
 sve to agreeable.

954
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:49,240
 Agreeable, da.

955
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:54,000
 Da više nemamo dobar ekvivalent tamo.

956
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,780
 Možda ima da se mi ne možemo osjetiti.

957
00:39:55,780 --> 00:39:56,380
 Možda ima, da.

958
00:39:56,380 --> 00:40:00,100
 Ali mislim da bi nekako naj...

959
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:01,900
 I što bi bila suprotnost uopće?

960
00:40:02,180 --> 00:40:04,680
 toj karakteristiki,

961
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:06,160
 karakteristici?

962
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:08,420
 Što bi bilo suprotno?

963
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:09,000
 Direktan?

964
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:12,000
 Ili netko ko...

965
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,080
 Pa znači, ako razmišljam kao...

966
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:15,280
 Hoći netko prihvaćan?

967
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,180
 Da.

968
00:40:16,180 --> 00:40:19,280
 Hoćeš li ići sa mnom na piće?

969
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:19,820
 Može.

970
00:40:19,820 --> 00:40:23,360
 Hoćeš li mi pomoć urediti studio?

971
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,160
 Hoću.

972
00:40:24,160 --> 00:40:25,600
 Hoćeš li...

973
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:26,860
 Znači, što god te neko pita,

974
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:27,480
 ti pristaneš.

975
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:27,900
 Da, da.

976
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:30,060
 To bi trebala biti ta osoba.

977
00:40:30,060 --> 00:40:31,480
 Da, Agreeable kao koja.

978
00:40:31,540 --> 00:40:32,640
 Da, ko prihvaća.

979
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:34,000
 Ko kaže na sve.

980
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,160
 Svi prihvaća.

981
00:40:35,160 --> 00:40:35,580
 Da, sve može.

982
00:40:35,580 --> 00:40:37,300
 U biti, možda više...

983
00:40:37,300 --> 00:40:41,400
 Možda nije nužno kontekst u prihvaćanju,

984
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:44,520
 nego prihvaća mimo sebe.

985
00:40:44,520 --> 00:40:47,480
 Što nema ništa lošo u tome da ti neko kažeš,

986
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,480
 nešto ti kažeš da.

987
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:52,520
 Možda si više Agreeable u tom kontekstu,

988
00:40:52,520 --> 00:40:56,520
 ako kažeš da i na stvari na koje možda ne bih htio reći da.

989
00:40:58,220 --> 00:40:59,640
 Znači, ja mislim da nemam ništa...

990
00:40:59,640 --> 00:41:00,840
 Što, šit samo na piće?

991
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,760
 Ako ja želim, da.

992
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:03,100
 Da li me to čini Agreeable?

993
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:05,380
 Ne, ja želim ić s tobom na piće.

994
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:07,640
 Činilo bi me ako ona...

995
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:08,900
 Znači, možda bih htio reći,

996
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,300
 je li ti, ili mi ti kažeš svoje mišlje?

997
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:11,860
 A, Slaveno, ja mislim da si ti glup.

998
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,060
 A da, da, je.

999
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:15,880
 Mislim, to jednu ruku isto Agreeable,

1000
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:18,540
 nemam nikako ništa da vratim,

1001
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:20,940
 nemam mišljenja o tome,

1002
00:41:20,940 --> 00:41:24,020
 nego samo slijedim ono što mi neko drugi govori.

1003
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:27,540
 Da li misliš da je ta karakteristika,

1004
00:41:27,540 --> 00:41:31,240
 recimo osobe koje prihvaća čak i ono što nije,

1005
00:41:31,240 --> 00:41:35,660
 u skladu sa onim što on želi, recimo,

1006
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:37,620
 i s njegovim stavima, uvjerenjima i tako dalje.

1007
00:41:37,620 --> 00:41:40,640
 Da li je to na nekakav način isto i pitanje toga

1008
00:41:40,640 --> 00:41:41,880
 da se ne poznaje dovoljno,

1009
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:44,840
 ili da fali vodlučnosti,

1010
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,840
 ili da fali samopouzdanje?

1011
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:49,200
 Hrabrosti.

1012
00:41:49,200 --> 00:41:50,300
 Hrabrosti?

1013
00:41:50,300 --> 00:41:53,080
 Da, mislim da...

1014
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:54,400
 Ali strah čega onda?

1015
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:57,980
 Strah povrđivanja te druge osobe ili nešto?

1016
00:41:57,980 --> 00:41:59,700
 Pa može biti,

1017
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:02,880
 To je uvratno dio nekakvog odrastanja ili traume

1018
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:07,080
 ili, ne znam, jednostavno kako te okolina oblikovala,

1019
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:12,120
 pa zato te strah vjerovat sebi i slušat sebe

1020
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:15,580
 možda kroz djetinstvo, kroz školu,

1021
00:42:15,580 --> 00:42:17,440
 kroz srednju, kroz fakultet.

1022
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:21,140
 Si bio kažnjan za to što si ti bio svoj

1023
00:42:21,140 --> 00:42:22,500
 ili nisi bio prihvaćan.

1024
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:25,160
 I on si se naučio adaptirati u principu da

1025
00:42:25,160 --> 00:42:28,920
 neću ja biti ja, nego ću ja prihvati što drugi misle

1026
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:31,960
 ili što drugi govore i što drugi mi kažu da treba napreti,

1027
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,020
 onda ću biti prihvaćen.

1028
00:42:33,020 --> 00:42:40,060
 I mislim da puno hrabrosti tu treba imat kad dolaziš iz takvog mindseta,

1029
00:42:40,060 --> 00:42:42,200
 gdje ti, isto koje na počešku smo pričali,

1030
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:43,860
 gdje ti osjetiš to.

1031
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:46,440
 Ti osjetiš potencijalno odbijanje,

1032
00:42:46,440 --> 00:42:48,820
 ti osjetiš da ti nećeš bit dio,

1033
00:42:48,820 --> 00:42:51,220
 ne znam, nekakvog kolektiva,

1034
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:53,540
 da nećeš biti shvaćen, da nećeš biti vidjen.

1035
00:42:53,540 --> 00:42:55,040
 Ti to osjetiš.

1036
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:58,780
 I sad, biti hrabar, poslušat sebe i reći ne,

1037
00:42:58,780 --> 00:43:01,100
 i riskirat biti odbačen od toga.

1038
00:43:01,100 --> 00:43:02,280
 To je ono,

1039
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:03,960
 velika stvar.

1040
00:43:04,360 --> 00:43:07,440
 Ja mogu zapravo dat nekako na svom primjeru,

1041
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:10,340
 znaš da sam bio u jednoj dugačkoj vezi.

1042
00:43:10,340 --> 00:43:10,940
 Da.

1043
00:43:10,940 --> 00:43:16,600
 I zapravo sam shvatio te kad sam izašao iz te veze,

1044
00:43:16,600 --> 00:43:18,400
 kad sam bio nekoliko godina sam,

1045
00:43:18,400 --> 00:43:22,280
 i ta veza je dosta dugo trala,

1046
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:23,860
 znači ja sam prekring,

1047
00:43:23,860 --> 00:43:27,260
 izašao sam iz te veze sa 30-ta godina,

1048
00:43:27,260 --> 00:43:28,720
 tako nešto rane, 30-te,

1049
00:43:28,720 --> 00:43:31,560
 i ja sam skušao da sam cijele 20-te proveo u vezi,

1050
00:43:31,560 --> 00:43:33,660
 da ja zapravo uopće nisam znao što ja želim.

1051
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:36,760
 Da sam jako puno kompromisa radio,

1052
00:43:36,760 --> 00:43:38,500
 možda sam i previše prihvaćao,

1053
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:41,080
 recimo ideje ili ono,

1054
00:43:41,080 --> 00:43:42,660
 što god, odluke te druge osobe,

1055
00:43:42,660 --> 00:43:43,920
 onako se priklanja,

1056
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:47,120
 možda išao linijom manjeg odpora ili što god.

1057
00:43:47,120 --> 00:43:50,360
 I onda sam se našao ono na nekoj vjetrometini,

1058
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:52,400
 onako da sam skužio kao, što ja želim?

1059
00:43:52,400 --> 00:43:53,420
 Tko sam ja.

1060
00:43:53,420 --> 00:43:54,220
 Tko sam ja.

1061
00:43:54,220 --> 00:43:58,680
 Sada ne idemo na one do ne najdublje razine duhovne,

1062
00:43:58,680 --> 00:43:59,800
 i tako dalje.

1063
00:43:59,800 --> 00:44:02,080
 Filozofski skroz kao tko sam ja,

1064
00:44:02,080 --> 00:44:04,260
 nego na ovaj nekoj svijetom,

1065
00:44:04,260 --> 00:44:05,320
 na razine tko sam ja,

1066
00:44:05,320 --> 00:44:06,280
 koji su moji interesi,

1067
00:44:06,280 --> 00:44:06,960
 što ja želim,

1068
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,040
 da li bi ovo me rekao da,

1069
00:44:08,040 --> 00:44:09,080
 ili bi ovo me rekao ne.

1070
00:44:09,080 --> 00:44:12,480
 Imaš nekako bolju mogućnost,

1071
00:44:12,480 --> 00:44:14,520
 jasnije to vidjeti kad si sam,

1072
00:44:14,520 --> 00:44:15,760
 kad nisi s nekim u vesijem.

1073
00:44:15,760 --> 00:44:17,820
 I kad si izvam toga odjednom.

1074
00:44:17,820 --> 00:44:28,660
 i ovaj, zapravo onda očito polaziš na točka toga da ne prihvaćaš stalno,

1075
00:44:28,660 --> 00:44:32,960
 nego da možeš biti odlučan, da možeš biti okej i hrabar.

1076
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:36,300
 Mislim, kako ćeš biti hrabar, uopće ako ne znaš šta želiš.

1077
00:44:37,940 --> 00:44:40,440
 Uglavnom su ti ljudi koji prihvaćaju sve,

1078
00:44:40,440 --> 00:44:41,520
 oni ne znaju tko su oni,

1079
00:44:41,520 --> 00:44:42,780
 po mojom mišljenju.

1080
00:44:43,320 --> 00:44:44,640
 I njima je sve okej.

1081
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:46,060
 Znači, idemo na Tajland.

1082
00:44:46,060 --> 00:44:46,880
 Ajmo na Tajland.

1083
00:44:46,880 --> 00:44:48,380
 Ajmo...

1084
00:44:48,380 --> 00:44:49,620
 Ja čak mislim suprotno.

1085
00:44:49,620 --> 00:44:50,360
 Ajde, suprotno.

1086
00:44:50,360 --> 00:44:50,760
 Ozmijeno.

1087
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:52,760
 Ja mislim da...

1088
00:44:52,760 --> 00:44:56,420
 Opet, znači, možda je to abstraktno,

1089
00:44:56,420 --> 00:44:57,740
 ali to je bio moj nekakav put.

1090
00:44:57,740 --> 00:45:02,520
 Ja mislim da svi mi znamo manje više tko smo,

1091
00:45:02,520 --> 00:45:04,820
 ili te neke osnovne stvari koje su nam bitne.

1092
00:45:04,820 --> 00:45:07,260
 I kad dođeš u situaciju da kažeš da,

1093
00:45:07,260 --> 00:45:08,640
 a da ne želiš reći da,

1094
00:45:08,640 --> 00:45:10,340
 ja mislim da se svjestom toga.

1095
00:45:10,340 --> 00:45:12,120
 Ali osjećaš možda tek nakon?

1096
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:14,020
 Da, da.

1097
00:45:14,020 --> 00:45:16,280
 Mislim, moguće je da osjetiš ti to i...

1098
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:19,020
 Čak i osjetiš i tad ja i ovom primjeru

1099
00:45:19,020 --> 00:45:21,600
 što sam dao kad sam pustio ovome da...

1100
00:45:21,600 --> 00:45:22,600
 Ja sam osjetio to.

1101
00:45:22,600 --> 00:45:24,380
 Ja nisam mogo prepoznat,

1102
00:45:24,380 --> 00:45:27,380
 nisam bio uviđavan toliko da skužim

1103
00:45:27,380 --> 00:45:29,960
 koja je to emocija, odakle ona dolazi.

1104
00:45:29,960 --> 00:45:31,860
 To možda nešto što treba vježbat.

1105
00:45:31,860 --> 00:45:34,840
 Ali znaš, ako ćemo pojednostavni stvari,

1106
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:37,360
 u nekom trenu, ako te neko pita

1107
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:38,220
 hoćeš li s nama,

1108
00:45:38,220 --> 00:45:41,620
 ja mislim da ti imaš vrlo jasan

1109
00:45:41,620 --> 00:45:43,600
 unutarnji osjećaj želim ili ne želim.

1110
00:45:43,600 --> 00:45:46,760
 Sad, možda ga ne znaš opisat

1111
00:45:46,760 --> 00:45:48,960
 zašto želim ili zašto ne želim,

1112
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:50,420
 to možda može doći kasnije.

1113
00:45:50,420 --> 00:45:52,020
 Ali mislim da ono,

1114
00:45:52,020 --> 00:45:54,620
 naučit slušat taj svoj

1115
00:45:54,620 --> 00:45:56,580
 i dat mu kredibilitet.

1116
00:45:56,580 --> 00:45:57,560
 Ono, okej, ne želim,

1117
00:45:57,560 --> 00:45:58,980
 pa možda ću ono,

1118
00:45:58,980 --> 00:46:00,780
 ili ću reći ne ide mi se,

1119
00:46:00,780 --> 00:46:02,680
 ili ću sad pa promisli zaš mi se ne ide.

1120
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:04,120
 ili ću svjesno onda oteći,

1121
00:46:04,120 --> 00:46:05,520
 pa vidi ti me to dovede.

1122
00:46:05,520 --> 00:46:08,640
 Ali ja iskreno mislim da

1123
00:46:08,640 --> 00:46:12,300
 svi mi u tom trenutku,

1124
00:46:12,300 --> 00:46:13,560
 recimo agreeable,

1125
00:46:13,560 --> 00:46:15,140
 kad kažeš da,

1126
00:46:15,140 --> 00:46:16,540
 možda želiš reći ne,

1127
00:46:16,540 --> 00:46:17,620
 ili kasnije misliš,

1128
00:46:17,620 --> 00:46:18,980
 osjetiš ti to,

1129
00:46:18,980 --> 00:46:21,020
 osjetiš da pristaješ na nešto

1130
00:46:21,020 --> 00:46:21,720
 što nije

1131
00:46:21,720 --> 00:46:24,280
 uravnoteženo možda s tobom.

1132
00:46:25,100 --> 00:46:27,660
 Ali neki ljudi su naučili

1133
00:46:27,660 --> 00:46:29,640
 tako se adaptirat,

1134
00:46:29,640 --> 00:46:31,200
 jer, kažem opet,

1135
00:46:31,200 --> 00:46:35,240
 svako je neki drugi put prolazio.

1136
00:46:35,240 --> 00:46:36,260
 Neko je ko djete,

1137
00:46:36,260 --> 00:46:37,300
 ne znam,

1138
00:46:37,300 --> 00:46:39,840
 pokušavao se zauzeti za sebe,

1139
00:46:39,840 --> 00:46:41,080
 pa je na jedan ili na drugi način

1140
00:46:41,080 --> 00:46:41,660
 bio kažnjen.

1141
00:46:41,660 --> 00:46:42,520
 Možda je od društva,

1142
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:43,780
 možda je došlo pa je rekao

1143
00:46:43,780 --> 00:46:45,240
 društvo, ja ne želim to sama.

1144
00:46:45,240 --> 00:46:46,720
 Pa su ga oni izopćili,

1145
00:46:46,720 --> 00:46:48,000
