1655
01:09:25,680 --> 01:09:28,720
 Te razine su pratili ono sve tako i blizance,

1656
01:09:28,720 --> 01:09:30,520
 pogotovo jer oni imaju isti denka.

1657
01:09:33,320 --> 01:09:35,040
