3373
01:58:28,960 --> 01:58:29,700
 kad bi ono rekli,

3374
01:58:29,700 --> 01:58:30,000
 ono,

3375
01:58:30,000 --> 01:58:30,280
 naš,

3376
01:58:30,280 --> 01:58:30,960
 brute force,

3377
01:58:30,960 --> 01:58:31,220
 ono,

3378
01:58:31,220 --> 01:58:34,180
 kako bi preveli brute force?

3379
01:58:35,240 --> 01:58:35,460
 Ono,

3380
01:58:35,460 --> 01:58:36,660
 velik, velik,

3381
01:58:36,660 --> 01:58:37,000
 znači,

3382
01:58:37,000 --> 01:58:37,920
 surovom silom.

3383
01:58:37,920 --> 01:58:42,680
 Surovom silom ču ja pretvoriti to u svoju realnost.

3384
01:58:42,680 --> 01:58:43,480
 Da, da.

